					<div id="contentSub"><div id="mw-content-subtitle"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">(Redirected from <a href="/w/index.php?title=Charles_Mills_(political_scientist)&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="Charles Mills (political scientist)">Charles Mills (political scientist)</a>)</span></div></div>
					
					
